==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mendelian
<hw>Men*de"li*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Mendel's law</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>Pert.
to <persfn>Mendel</persfn>, or to Mendel's law; <as>as,
<ex>Mendelian</ex> inheritance</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>Behaving or being in accordance
with Mendel's laws of inheritance; -- said of the distribution of
inherited characteristics and of traits thus distributed.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Men*de"li*an*ism</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>, <wf>Men*del"ism</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mendelian character</ent>⟦br⟧
